net.proteusframework.internet.servlet.filter.compression

Class TimedOutputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • java.io.FilterOutputStream
        • net.proteusframework.internet.servlet.filter.compression.TimedOutputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Flushable, AutoCloseable

    class TimedOutputStream
extends FilterOutputStream
    Records the amount of time spent writing. This class should be wrapped in turn by a BufferedOutputStream so that block writes are done.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
